org.wikidata.wdtk.rdf

Class WikidataPropertyTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wikidata.wdtk.rdf.WikidataPropertyTypes
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PropertyTypes

    public class WikidataPropertyTypes
extends Object
implements PropertyTypes
    This class helps to manage the exact datatype of properties used in an RDF dump. It caches known types and fetches type information from the Web if needed.
    Author:
    Markus Kroetzsch
